--- This ltx gives all guns recoil stats based on a calculation I came up with
--- I gave a "standard" to each rifle design and caliber, so a 5.56 bullpup is similar across the board, a 5.56 traditional rifle is similar, 545, etc...
--- The goal is aside from PCCs/SMGs, sustained full auto isn't viable at distance. CQB sure but outside you'll want to use semi-auto fire.

;=============================================================
;-------------------------Pistols----------------------
;=============================================================

